official_title: Detection of Breast Lesions Utilizing iBreast Exam: A Comparison With Clinical Breast Exam
inclusion_criteria:
* Female patient
* Over 18 years of age, able to consent
* RLC patients presenting to RLC or BAIC for mammogram and CBE
* Asymptomatic and symptomatic patients will be included
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Male patients
* Patients under 18 years of age, unable to consent
* Pregnant patients
* Lactating patients
* Non-intact skin
